-All right.<br>-Okay.
<SYNC Start=851648><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=852017><P Class=ENCC>
I write erotic novels..
<SYNC Start=854781><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=854954><P Class=ENCC>
for children.
<SYNC Start=856512><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=859158><P Class=ENCC>
-What?<br>-They're wildly unpopular.
<SYNC Start=861752><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=862595><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, my God!
<SYNC Start=864495><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=864663><P Class=ENCC>
Also, you might like to know<br>I have a Ph.D.
<SYNC Start=867496><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=867666><P Class=ENCC>
-Wow! You do?<br>-Yep. A pretty huge..
<SYNC Start=870567><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=870736><P Class=ENCC>
All right.
<SYNC Start=872135><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=888254><P Class=ENCC>
-Hey.<br>-Joey, honey, listen.
<SYNC Start=890154><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=890322><P Class=ENCC>
Thanks for talking to me yesterday.<br>It meant a lot.
<SYNC Start=893917><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=894093><P Class=ENCC>
Not a problem.<br>Just so you know..
<SYNC Start=896323><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=896495><P Class=ENCC>
that guy won't be bothering<br>you about that baby thing anymore.
<SYNC Start=900989><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=902835><P Class=ENCC>
-What?<br>-Let's just say I took care of it.
<SYNC Start=905599><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=906372><P Class=ENCC>
Let's say more.
<SYNC Start=908636><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=908807><P Class=ENCC>
Don't worry. I told him, very nicely:
<SYNC Start=911970><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=912144><P Class=ENCC>
"You don't go buying people's babies!<br>So back off!"
<SYNC Start=916012><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=916181><P Class=ENCC>
-What?<br>-What?
<SYNC Start=918445><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=918617><P Class=ENCC>
No, no, no!
<SYNC Start=919845><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=920019><P Class=ENCC>
He doesn't want to buy my baby!<br>I made that up!
<SYNC Start=923113><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
