<SYNC Start=943139><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=944376><P Class=ENCC>
I can't believe you brought<br>my boss into it! I'll be fired!
<SYNC Start=948312><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=948480><P Class=ENCC>
-You lied to me!<br>-Well, she told me to!
<SYNC Start=951415><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=952885><P Class=ENCC>
Chandler has two copies of Annie!
<SYNC Start=956048><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=995961><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, my God!
<SYNC Start=997189><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=997896><P Class=ENCC>
-Ross!<br>-Hello!
<SYNC Start=1001297><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1002234><P Class=ENCC>
What are you doing?
<SYNC Start=1003701><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1003869><P Class=ENCC>
Not touching myself, if that makes<br>anyone less uncomfortable.
<SYNC Start=1009774><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1010009><P Class=ENCC>
Okay, then. I'll call you.
<SYNC Start=1011601><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1024757><P Class=ENCC>
