<SYNC Start=1027248><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1027426><P Class=ENCC>
Please, come in. Have a seat.
<SYNC Start=1030293><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1032598><P Class=ENCC>
-Look, Mr. Zelner..<br>-It's best I speak first.
<SYNC Start=1035590><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1035768><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah.
<SYNC Start=1036996><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1038804><P Class=ENCC>
Lee from Human Resources is here<br>as a witness to our conversation.
<SYNC Start=1043798><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1044076><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, God.
<SYNC Start=1045475><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1046445><P Class=ENCC>
If I in any way implied<br>that I wanted to buy your baby..
<SYNC Start=1052645><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1055020><P Class=ENCC>
I am sorry. Okay?
<SYNC Start=1057113><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1057289><P Class=ENCC>
Last week, when I asked you<br>when your due date was..
<SYNC Start=1060850><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1061026><P Class=ENCC>
I certainly did not mean that<br>I felt that I was "due" your baby.
<SYNC Start=1066430><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1068467><P Class=ENCC>
I want to be very clear..
<SYNC Start=1070799><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1070969><P Class=ENCC>
that I understand<br>that it's your baby..
<SYNC Start=1074302><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1074807><P Class=ENCC>
and it is not mine to purchase.
<SYNC Start=1078334><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1084249><P Class=ENCC>
Well, as long as we are clear<br>about that.
<SYNC Start=1087776><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
