<SYNC Start=1310036><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1310942><P Class=ENCC>
Anyway, Mona, I'm really, really sorry.<br>It's just..
<SYNC Start=1314002><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1314179><P Class=ENCC>
